    "description": "<p>PolyAquol™-OS2, a patented, naturally derived W/O polyglycerol self-emulsifier, perfect for creating cold-processed emulsions with a light texture and pleasant skin feel. Certified by Ecocert and Cosmos, it ensures high natural standards. PolyAquol™-OS2 is compatible with silicone derivatives and boosts the performance of other emulsifiers. Its excellent dispersing abilities for powders and pigments make it ideal for sun-care and makeup formulations. Whether you're formulating sunscreens or cosmetics, PolyAquol™-OS2 provides superior stability and texture, ensuring your products meet both performance and natural ingredient demands.</p>",
